s,\ncausing large unbounded DB reads (e.g. OrgUnit.users = 1015 rows,\nUserRole.members = 222k rows).\n\nThree guards in DefaultMetadataMergeService.merge():\n- Skip collection properties with no setter method (read-only computed\n  views such as UserRole.getUsers()). No setter means the merge result\n  would be discarded anyway.\n- Move targetObject load (which triggers lazy init) to after the\n  sourceObject == null early-return.\n- Skip uninitialized Hibernate PersistentCollections before addAll.\n\nOne guard in DefaultPreheatService.collectObjectReferences():\n- Skip collection references that are not yet initialized.\n\nPlain Java collections are always considered initialized; only Hibernate\nproxy collections that have not yet been fetched are skipped.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e","author":{"name":"Jason Pickering","email":"jason@dhis2.org"},"id":"bcaae8b52e3a83e5417ed3d7e1ef57c9a3f34727","tree_id":"10b109c8d1470c22053cfe201bc364b4b6d1c2b8","timestamp":"2026-03-03T17:58:06Z","committer":{"name":"Jason Pickering","email":"jason@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/10954","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/us